Isamu KOBAYASHI, Appellant, v. John D. NAGLE, Commissioner of Immigration, Port of San Francisco, California, Appellee. No. 6424. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 18, 1932. Philip M. Zwerin and George R. Andersen, both of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. Geo. J. Hatfield, U. S. Atty., and H. A. Tan Der Zee, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of San Francisco, Cal, for appellee.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellant, or-, dered appeal dismissed.
